23:30.272 --> 23:35.357
people, legitimate maybe a repertory group here 
or something like that, but that will come. How

23:39.045 --> 23:42.289
about university-type complexes or 
educational? Terribly important, sure, because

23:42.349 --> 23:56.525
if you had a university out here and you can 
participate in the cultural life of the

23:42.349 --> 23:56.525
university and mix with some of those people who 
are living here, it makes it a fuller life. I spent a

23:59.008 --> 24:03.353
lot of time in Palm Springs, and I wouldn't spend 
the time there if it weren't for the fact We have a

