32:19.074 --> 32:26.362
universal, consistent theme of the collection of 
art. See, if I were starting fresh, I would have

32:27.043 --> 32:30.987
nothing but Southwestern art here. by great 
Southwestern artists and sculptors. At this

32:36.048 --> 32:39.412
point, I feel that the collection is kind of 
random. Somebody saw something, and they bought

32:39.633 --> 32:42.196
it, and they like it. It's a little apocalyptic. 
